OL,3,CTeenager in life-threatening condition
OL,4,Cafter being stabbed in Ilford
OL,6,FA teenager has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder after a
OL,8,F15-year-old boy was stabbed in Ilford.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Ilford Lane at
OL,11,Faround 4.55pm on Saturday, June 13,
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of a stabbing.
OL,14,FOfficers attended alongside the London
OL,15,FAmbulance Service, and the victim was
OL,16,Ftreated at the scene for stab injuries
OL,17,Fbefore being taken to hospital.
OL,19,FThe 15-year-old remains in a life-
OL,20,Fthreatening condition.
