OL,3,CTeenager in life-threatening condition
OL,4,Cafter being stabbed in Ilford
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of attempted murder and
OL,8,Fremains in police custody.
OL,10,FPolice are appealing for witnesses.
OL,11,FAnyone who saw the incident is asked
OL,12,Fto call 101, quoting reference 5194/
OL,13,F13JUN.
